n ㅋㅋ https://t.co/DxBvdSSQUz", "time": "12:24", "author": "antonisbabo", "author_name": "바보", "followers": 39618, "views": 13842, "likes": 798, "replies": 0, "retweets": 282, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 79, "labels": {"relevant": false, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": []}}, {"id": "2071949563267575948", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2071949563267575948", "text": "CHART OF THE DAY: The global energy system, split by regions and source (from the annual @EnergyInstitute 'Statistical Review of World Energy,' celebrating this year its 75th edition). Do look at that big chunk of grey at the center of the chart — that's coal (China and India). https://t.co/h4jrG6LY", "time": "13:30", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 43936, "likes": 247, "replies": 19, "retweets": 81, "quotes": 18, "bookmarks": 88, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["China demand"]}}, {"id": "2071950413876609186", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2071950413876609186", "text": "The full report is here: https://t.co/7bX5pmrAqU", "time": "13:34", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 10665, "likes": 20, "replies": 1, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 15, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": []}}, {"id": "2071963751872368745", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2071963751872368745", "text": "BP deputy CEO (and head of trading) Carol Howle is retiring 3 months after she was promoted to the deputy job. \n\nThe company says that was always the plan, although BP didn’t indicate it was a short-term appointment when her new title was announced. Sam Skerry takes over as head of trading.", "time": "14:27", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 53211, "likes": 143, "replies": 13, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 14, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Oil majors"]}}, {"id": "2071964819566313961", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2071964819566313961", "text": "Iran May be building floating storage near Singapore \n\nIf so, it may be because they expect prices to rise in the near term #oott", "time": "14:31", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 16334, "likes": 89, "replies": 10, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 10, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2071984422174220735", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071984422174220735", "text": "US crude production was at 13.934mbpd in April vs 13.718mbpd in March (revised from 13.696)\nm/m changes in kbpd\n\nUS +216\n\nGulf of America/Mexico +119\nNew Mexico +65\nTexas +36\nNorth Dakota +8\nOhio +6\nOklahoma -12\n\nEIA #oott", "time": "15:49", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 24402, "likes": 33, "replies": 1, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Shale/US production"]}}, {"id": "2071985431739077097", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071985431739077097", "text": "No Brent crude oil cargoes set to load in August, a first for global price benchmark  #oott https://t.co/IvWfcKZLCb", "time": "15:53", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 30188, "likes": 135, "replies": 7, "retweets": 29, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2072011769740997078", "url": "https://x.com/TankerTrackers/status/2072011769740997078", "text": "Iran has exported 50 million barrels of crude oil since the US-imposed blockade was lifted two weeks ago. This equates to 1.66 million barrels per day for June 2026. Most other countries in the region are still nowhere near pre-war levels.\n\n#OOTT #IranWar #Tankers https://t.co/FJb70n0lbx", "time": "17:37", "author": "TankerTrackers", "author_name": "TankerTrackers.com, Inc.", "followers": 227035, "views": 158008, "likes": 541, "replies": 30, "retweets": 145, "quotes": 24, "bookmarks": 84, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2072012991394898122", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2072012991394898122", "text": "Another awfully weak trading day in the physical oil windows. Even after sellers offered the largest ever discounts for some WAF crudes, buyers are not emerging. In the North Sea, physical premia for some grades hit a fresh 6-year low.", "time": "17:42", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 90923, "likes": 501, "replies": 35, "retweets": 45, "quotes": 8, "bookmarks": 49, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Prices/technicals", "Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2072019228081754333", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2072019228081754333", "text": "US oil demand was up 595kbpd or 2.9% y/y to 20.808mbpd in April, a new record high for the month of April - EIA #oott https://t.co/2DGs6orE0W", "time": "18:07", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 16745, "likes": 34, "replies": 1, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2072046145992565015", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2072046145992565015", "text": "Danish authorities have dropped a high profile case against a group of energy traders for alleged market manipulation. \n\nThe case, dating back to 2023, shocked the close-knit world of electricity and gas trading in Aarhus, the Danish town considered the Silicon Valley of European energy trading. \n\nh", "time": "19:54", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 36181, "likes": 136, "replies": 9, "retweets": 18, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 44, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Natural gas"]}}, {"id": "2072047956799463656", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2072047956799463656", "text": "US total oil production -- and crude output -- rose to a record high in April, according to revised @EIAgov data.\n\nThe monthly data pegs US total oil output at 21.836m b/d in April (up 565,000 b/d from the initial estimate for the month based on weekly data). On an annual basis, US total oil product", "time": "20:01", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 32017, "likes": 149, "replies": 13, "retweets": 28, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Shale/US production"]}}, {"id": "2072049965728194758", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2072049965728194758", "text": "#Iran’s Diverging Priorities Are Jeopardizing U.S. Peace Talks\nModerates are eager to free up billions of dollars held in Qatar, but hard-liners are focused on controlling the Strait of Hormuz #oott https://t.co/fn1ed6jBKL", "time": "20:09", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 12240, "likes": 10, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2072060074365698538", "url": "https://x.